5)Invalid Credentials will show error message as : Invalid Credentials :-
 
6)Any field empty then will get proper message for that in css as well in text format:-
 
7)After login successfully as per above shared credentials .You ll redirect to home screen:-
 
1)You can see that company details section -
  1.All the company details getting from backend api.
2)You can see that  contact details section -
1]All the contact details getting from backend api.
2]All the edit , update, delete functionality calling backend api
Details about Subsection:-
1.Add New Contact:- In contact details there is plus button :- on clicking on that button you can add new contact details with required validation
 
2.Edit Contact:-In contact details there is edit button ,On clicking on that you can edit existing contact .
 
3.Delete Contact:-In contact details section there is remove button, On clicking on that you can remove the contact from the list.

8)Logout button:- Once clicked on logout user ll logout successfully and redirect to login page
